OL,3,C'I've done nothing wrong': Man wrongly
OL,4,Cfined in NCP car park
OL,6,FA man from Bridgend says the industry
OL,7,Fneeds to change after he was wrongly
OL,8,Fcharged for overstaying in a private
OL,9,Fcar park.
OL,11,FRhodri Davies was fined for being in
OL,12,Fan NCP car park in Cardiff, despite
OL,13,Fhaving proof that he left before the
OL,14,Ftiming restrictions applied.
OL,16,FDavies had driven into the Adam Street
OL,17,FNCP car park, but left quickly after
OL,18,Fseeing long queues at the pay machine.
OL,19,FHe then drove to an alternative car
OL,20,Fpark.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
