FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779462669
OL,3,C'I've done nothing wrong': Man wrongly
OL,4,Cfined in NCP car park
OL,6,FBut shortly after, he received an NCP
OL,7,Fparking fine.
OL,9,FDavies told ITV News he was shocked to
OL,10,Freceive the charge: "I saw I had a
OL,11,Fparking charge notice, I thought
OL,12,F'that's for Adam Street,' I wasn't
OL,13,Fparked in Adam Street, I was only
OL,14,Fthere for a couple of minutes."
OL,16,FIn their notice to Davies, NCP claimed
OL,17,Fthat their number plate recognition
OL,18,Fcameras detected he was in their car
OL,19,Fpark for nearly 20 minutes, from the
OL,20,Ftimings of 6:01pm-6:19pm.
OL,26,@rD@UOUvD@_O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779462669
OL,3,C'I've done nothing wrong': Man wrongly
OL,4,Cfined in NCP car park
OL,6,FBut after doing his own investigation,
OL,7,FDavies was able to show that his
OL,8,Fvehicle was in the second car park by
OL,9,F6:10pm, proving that NCP's fine was
OL,10,Fincorrectly issued.
OL,12,FThe fine was cancelled after Davies
OL,13,Fappealed but he has described the
OL,14,Fordeal as "frustrating":
OL,16,F"I knew I was being accused of
OL,17,Fsomething that wasn't true. We
OL,18,Fshouldn't be penalised and fined when
OL,19,Fwe've done nothing wrong.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779462669
OL,3,C'I've done nothing wrong': Man wrongly
OL,4,Cfined in NCP car park
OL,6,F"You need to have enough time to find
OL,7,Fa parking space, to use the machine,
OL,8,Fand to read the terms and conditions,
OL,9,Fand to accept those terms and
OL,10,Fconditions, and if you don't, it's
OL,11,Fyour right to leave", he told ITV News.
OL,13,FLisa Webb, a lawyer at Which?,
OL,14,Fexplained the problems in NCP's
OL,15,Freliance on CCTV: "These automatic
OL,16,Fnumber plate recognition cameras are
OL,17,Fabout 97% reliable, but that means
OL,18,Fthat there are still millions of cars
OL,19,Fper year that are getting incorrectly
OL,20,Frecorded by these cameras.
OL,26,@wD@SOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779462669
OL,3,C'I've done nothing wrong': Man wrongly
OL,4,Cfined in NCP car park
OL,6,F"The fact that they can be wrong needs
OL,7,Fto be acknowledged by these companies.
OL,8,FIt shouldn't be down to the consumer
OL,9,Fto fight their corner if the
OL,10,Ftechnology being used isn't accurate
OL,11,Fin the first place."
OL,13,FA spokesperson for NCP said they are
OL,14,Finvestigating the ANPR data for Adam
OL,15,FStreet.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
