OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779462669
OL,3,C'I've done nothing wrong': Man wrongly
OL,4,Cfined in NCP car park
OL,6,F"We thank Mr Davies for bringing his
OL,7,Fexperience to our attention and, as we
OL,8,Fhave confirmed to him directly, NCP
OL,9,Fare currently investigating this
OL,10,Finternally. We take these types of
OL,11,Fconcerns extremely seriously and
OL,12,Fshould we find any discrepancies then
OL,13,Fwe will contact any customer who has
OL,14,Fbeen impacted by this."
